<h2>Why am I being pursued for unpaid service charges?</h2>

<p>
Under the terms of your lease/transfer agreement, you are <u>required</u> to pay ground rent and service charges.
</p>

<p>
We are writing to you as your non-payment of service charges and ground rent totalling £<%= @letter.lba_balance %> is a breach of these terms.
</p>

